    %h2#whatsup What is this project?
    %p.summary
      Pairprogram.com provides an easy way for programmers to meet up and program together.
      Once you provide your location you will see a list of programmers available to pair in your area.
      If you'd like to pair with one of them, you can send a message.  If they are amenable, they will 
      respond and you can arrange a time and a place.
      = link_to "Okay, sounds good!", root_path

